review 5:
Just a perfect place to stay in Bali.

name: Agung Village
address: Gang capung, Jl. Dukuh Jl. Tanah Lot, Beraban, Kec. Kediri, Kabupaten Tabanan, Bali 82121, Indonesia
review 1:

Service wasn't always on site, but contactable by phone.
